  <official_title>A Two-Stage Randomized Placebo-controlled Ascending Dose Phase I/ IIa Study to Evaluate Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacodynamic Effects and Preliminary Efficacy of an Anti-Interleukin 1 Beta Vaccine (CYT013-IL1bQb) in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus</official_title>
